This is the Go implementation of the Noahcoin protocol. It's for from being finished.

The Python reference implementation can be found at https://github.com/vbuterin/pynoahcoin

More information about the protocol:
* http://vitalik.ca/noahcoin.html
* http://vitalik.ca/noahcoin/spec.html
* http://vitalik.ca/noahcoin/patricia.html
* http://vitalik.ca/noahcoin/dagger.html
* http://vitalik.ca/noahcoin/rlp.html

